cs.MM, cs.CR, cs.CV, cs.IT, cs.SI 

The paper discusses multimedia data security, specifically video encryption algorithms. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.MM (Multimedia). The paper also discusses cryptographic security, which falls under cs.CR (Cryptography and Security). The analysis and comparison of algorithms with respect to visual degradation and compression friendliness suggest that the paper may also belong to cs.CV (Computer Vision) and cs.IT (Information Theory). Finally, the paper's focus on encryption and security may also place it in cs.SI (Social and Information Networks).
